"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搭左成3粒鐘<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/201710_c8f9fae97592087a285f5c2a294e1381.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F201710_c8f9fae97592087a285f5c2a294e1381.jpg&h=e5009855&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搭無人去另一個terminal <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/201740_d4adb184753e9b36cbb09c5b7e5c1852.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F201740_d4adb184753e9b36cbb09c5b7e5c1852.jpg&h=1cdd4bb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有冇人覺得好似新加坡聖淘沙個express<br />\n<br />\n終於到<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/201932_b67bf3b18a3d000d877eac593230394a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F201932_b67bf3b18a3d000d877eac593230394a.jpg&h=cc5d4d52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個機場好舊 好似去左台中咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/202123_25db25bc34b087555df4145c9179c1a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F202123_25db25bc34b087555df4145c9179c1a5.jpg&h=e1281ccd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n地勤姐姐<br />\n好撚煩 比人係咁點黎點去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有櫃檯d人又唔想做 西口西面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n入到閘去到duty free<br />\n瘋狂買煙酒 yo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/202351_fa10e101fb5fe98a59abaaeecbef3511.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F202351_fa10e101fb5fe98a59abaaeecbef3511.jpg&h=de66e8a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為我地坐廉航 去垃圾wagamama買垃圾上機食<br />\n(唔知點解up唔到呢張圖）<br />\n講真 唔係我唔想買飛機d野食 係你得sandwiches/salad<br />\n我坐8粒鐘啊 想餓死我咩<br />\n比個意粉黎賣我$10加紙我都冇所謂<br />\n$7加紙一個sandwiches真係食唔飽我sor<br />\n你屌我乞衣都係咁話<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家終於上到機 冇電視 窄位<br />\n希望平安渡過8個鐘 訓個靚覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n8個鐘後見"},{"pid":"0221b35bcb64f6a4cb53ecc82b6e72e9fbdf6738","tid":283432,"uid":360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T12:31:15.000Z","msg":"補多張圖<br />\n我163 個位真係好窄 但有usb頭<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/203113_a0848eaa054c52678afc894ba0d3763c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F203113_a0848eaa054c52678afc894ba0d3763c.jpg&h=9cacea2a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b529a2ed45b1c1ed7a18e01fd096d4a7cd01557d","tid":283432,"uid":25038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T13:28:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1bb1ec48334a09963f294ae7aca5d2d62f8167","tid":283432,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T13:38:39.000Z","msg":"加拿大遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f8a4e607b9783a6e1846ebd4b65dfeff4db55d5","tid":283432,"uid":360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T16:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比左一舊水港紙係飛機上網 上黎say個hi<br />\n仲有4粒鐘 同隔離廢青係咁鬧交 關於訓覺姿勢問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n頭好痛啊 比我訓啦"},{"pid":"4315e2bd2d3a85ab4b97e0c1765c275a7c9c8387","tid":283432,"uid":360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T20:52:03.000Z","msg":"終於到左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/044847_db0161d63ecd72e668fb8a536cf2cef8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https: